<HEADLINE>
FT  20 JAN 94 / The FT500 (41): UK Top 500 - Largest falls to loss
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
 -----------------------------------------------------------------------
UK TOP 500 - LARGEST FALLS TO LOSS
 -----------------------------------------------------------------------
   Company                    Sector   UK500 rank   Pounds m
 -----------------------------------------------------------------------
 1 Imperial Chemical Industries  622           28    -1227.0
 2 British Aerospace             523           91    -1089.0
 3 Barclays                      112           18     -775.0
 4 Saatchi &amp; Saatchi             475          245     -542.7
 5 Tarmac                        613          109     -371.3
 6 Lasmo                         213          129     -268.0
 7 Rolls-Royce                   521           83     -235.0
 8 Wimpey (George)               613          189      -96.3
