<HEADLINE>
FT  20 JAN 94 / World News in Brief: British MP praises Saddam
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
A British opposition Labour party member of parliament, George Galloway, was
disowned by his party leader John Smith after appearing on Iraqi television,
praising President Saddam Hussein's 'courage' and 'power'.
